  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onions and garlic, sauté until softened and translucent.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, smoked paprika, coriander powder, and turmeric powder. Cook for another minute.",
    "Pour in the fermented black beans and water, mix well to combine.",
    "Simmer on medium-low heat for about 10 minutes or until sauce thickens slightly.",
    "Serve hot with your favorite side dishes."
